snippet.title: GOONL!NE - Grand Theft Auto IV:  The Lost and Damned [Video Game Awards 2008] [HD]
snippet.description:
The Lost and Damned are on their way.

Grand Theft Auto IV: The Lost and Damned, the first of two DLC episodes, will be coming to Grand Theft Auto IV in February 2009, exclusively for the Xbox 360.
